Well.. I Just Made One Of My First Rsps.. And I Add A Bunch Of Customs, All Of Them Are Perfectly Working.. BUT.. They Have 0 In Every Stats.

[IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/13z5wch.jpg[/img] Btw Its Not The Name, My Item Name Is Actually "NoNamedItem" Rofl.
What Did I Do Wrong?
P.s.. Please Don't Call Me Or Retarded Or W-e Cus Its Simple To Fix.. Like I Said.. (I'm New In Coding)
Need Help Quick, Thx.
